1. Moj *zeleni* džemper je nov. (My *green* sweater is new.)
2. Ovo *zeleno* povrće je jako ukusno. (This *green* vegetable is very tasty.)
3. Ona *zeleni* paprike u vrtu. (She *grows* green peppers in her garden.)
4. *Zelenilo* oko kuće je veoma lepo. (The *greenery* around the house is very beautiful.)
5. Da li si videla *zelenkaste* oči te devojke? (Have you seen the *greenish* eyes of that girl?)
6. Oni su *ozelenili* park u centru grada. (They *greened* the park in the city center.)
7. U prodavnici sam kupio *zeleniš* za salatu. (I bought *greens* for a salad at the store.)
8. Ujutru volim da popijem *zeleni* čaj. (In the morning, I like to drink *green* tea.)
9. *Zeleno* svetlo na semaforu znači da možemo da krenemo. (The *green* light on the traffic light means we can go.)
10. *Zelenjenje* planete je važno pitanje za celu civilizaciju. (The *greening* of the planet is an important issue for the entire civilization.)